Package: EVSI
Title: EVSI: Calculating the Expected Value of Sample Information
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Date: 2017-09-01
Authors@R: c(person("Anna", "Heath", email = "anna.heath.14@ucl.ac.uk", role = c("aut", "cre")),
             person("Gianluca", "Baio", email= "g.baio@ucl.ac.uk", role="aut"))
Description: Given a health economic model, including a full probablisitic sensitivity analysis, and a study design, the EVSI can be calculated using the Moment Matching method. A suite of graphics are then provided, including a web application that allows for dynamic plotting to aid decision making.
Depends: R (>= 3.2.1)
Suggests: rjags, BCEA, R2OpenBUGS, shiny, shinythemes
License: GPL (>=2)
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 6.1.1
